name: Kid, you'll move mountains - A4 or A3 - Black
description:
Another print inspired by my favourite kids book Dr Seuss's 'Oh, the places you'll go'. This quote also aims to inspire and motivate young or old(er)! A great addition to any space and a match to our very popular 'Oh the places you'll go!' prints.

Has a lovely texture through the text which is a result of it being hand drawn using watercolour paints. High quality digital print on 300gsm fine textured crisp white, archival and acid free paper. Also available in navy blue.

Size: A4 (210mm x 297mm) or A3 (297mm x 420mm).

Shipped in a cellophane sleeve (with a cardboard backing), within a hard ridged envelope.

description:

This is a beautiful specialty print, incorporating gold foil, and is our first limited edition to our range.

High quality offset printed on 280gsm textured white, archival and acid free paper. Being gold foil blocked no one print is exactly the same so yours will definitely be unique to you! Each of these limited edition prints of 250 are signed and numbered on the front. Get one while you can!!!

Size: A4 (210mm x 297mm or 8.27" x 11.69").

Note: Due to the process of gold foiling on this stock, a slight textured
effect may occur on the bottom of the print.

Shipped in a cellophane sleeve (with a cardboard backing), within a hard ridged envelope.

name: Haere Mai everything is Ka Pai - A4
description:
A custom geometric typeface, inspired by Maori patterns and the song title of the 1952 original by Sam Freedman. The song was designed to welcome tourists to New Zealand and in preparation for the visit from Queen Elizabeth II who was to tour the country the following year.

This high quality, elegant artwork is offset printed on 300gsm white archival and acid free stock, using metallic gold ink to make it even more special!

Size: A4 (210mm x 297mm or 8.27" x 11.69").

Shipped in a cellophane sleeve with a cardboard backing, within a hard ridged envelope.

The perfect art piece for every Kiwi home.

name: You're Special* - A2
description:

Bring a cheer to your home with this tongue-in-cheek fluorescent orange poster. Not your average Specials sign.

High quality, offset printed poster on 250gsm white archival and acid free stock, using fluorescent orange ink to make it even more special!

Size: A2 (420mm x 594mm or 16.5" x 23.4"). 

Shipped carefully rolled in tissue paper, within a sturdy, large diameter (101mm) white tube.

Note: due to the nature of the fluoro inks, it is pretty hard to represent the actual colour digitally! Please take care when removing the print from the tube. Like all prints, keep away from direct sunlight - especially this one or the fluorescent colour will fade.

name: Height Chart - Animals
description:
* GROWING UP WITH STYLE *  Animals galore - helping make learning to count lots of fun. These stylish height charts are the perfect way to keep track of every little growth spurt!

Unlike other growth charts which are often aimed at very young children, our bright contemporary designs mean your child will enjoy them for many years.

Two measurement scales - centimeters & inches. Record how tall you have grown, right up to 150cm or 59. The height chart measure 290mm x 1000mm. Printed on a 300gsm glossy stock. Comes packaged in a sturdy white tube and shipped within a bag.

The lightweight and rollable chart make it a fantastic gift idea and great keepsake for years to come.
